                <p style="color: #4b5563; margin-bottom: 1rem; font-style: italic;">Partner-driven interventions that address hidden dynamics, not add more capacity.</p>
                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-6">
                    <div class="focus-card">
                        <div class="focus-card-icon">üìä</div>
                        <h4 class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Energy Services Framing</h4>
