                            <li><strong>Investment opportunity:</strong> Station area redesign, feeder integration, e-rickshaw fleets</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <div class="mb-4">
                        <h4 class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">The EV Transition Trap</h4>
