                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
                    <div>
                        <h4 class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">1. Embodied Carbon Accountability</h4>
                        <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mb-2"><strong>Problem:</strong> 40% of emissions ignored by policy <a href="resources.html#ref-aeee-embodied-carbon-2024" class="text-xs text-primary hover:underline" title="AEEE Embodied Carbon Report">[51]</a></p>
