                        <h4 class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">2. ECBC Enforcement via TPA Ecosystem</h4>
                        <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mb-2"><strong>Problem:</strong> 23 states notified, &lt;5 enforce <a href="resources.html#ref-bee-ecbc-compliance-2023" class="text-xs text-primary hover:underline" title="ECBC Compliance Report">[5]</a></p>
