                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">üîç Hidden Dynamics: The Systemic Barriers</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 italic mb-4">These systemic issues don't appear in official statistics but determine whether interventions succeed or fail. Investment here creates leverage.</p>
                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
                    <div>
                        <h4 class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">1. Ownership & Demands</h4>
