                <p style="color: #4b5563; margin-bottom: 1rem; font-style: italic;">India has 4,000+ processing plants but only 25% operate at capacity. The problem isn't technology ‚Äî it's incentives, data integrity, and who captures value.</p>
                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-6">
