                            <li><strong>WtE lock-in:</strong> ‚Çπ500+ Cr plants need feedstock forever ‚Äî lobby against recycling</li>
                            <li><strong>Partner opportunity:</strong> Outcome-based contracts, recycling-first mandates</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <div class="mb-4">
                        <h4 class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">3. Informal Sector Paradox</h4>
