                            <li><strong>Formalization backfires:</strong> Company contracts exclude pickers, rates drop</li>
                            <li><strong>Value extraction:</strong> Aggregators capture 90%; pickers get 5-10%</li>
                            <li><strong>Partner opportunity:</strong> Picker-owned cooperatives, direct market access</li>
