                    <div class="mb-4">
                        <h4 class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">5. Political Economy</h4>
                        <ul class="text-sm">
                            <li><strong>Land mafia nexus:</strong> Dumpsites on valuable land; remediation unlocks real estate</li>
