                            <li><strong>Partner opportunity:</strong> Independent remediation verification, ring-fenced funds</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <div class="mb-4">
                        <h4 class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">6. Supply Obsession</h4>
